OL,3,CChildren 'being failed in dual crises
OL,4,Cof poverty and mental health'
OL,6,FChildren are being failed in "dual
OL,7,Fcrises of poverty and mental health",
OL,8,Faccording to charities which have
OL,9,Framped up calls for the Government to
OL,10,Fscrap the two-child benefit limit.
OL,12,FThe groups said money and mental
OL,13,Fhealth are "inextricably linked" and
OL,14,Fthat those children growing up in
OL,15,Ffamilies facing financial hardship
OL,16,Fface a knock-on impact throughout
OL,17,Ftheir lives.
