OL,6,FThe report from the Centre for Mental
OL,7,FHealth, Save the Children UK and the
OL,8,FChildren and Young People's Mental
OL,9,FHealth Coalition recommended the new
OL,10,FLabour Government should scrap both
OL,11,Fthe two-child limit and the benefit
OL,12,Fcap "to ensure all children receive
OL,13,Ftheir benefit entitlements".
