OL,6,FPressure has been growing on Prime
OL,7,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer to axe the
OL,8,Ftwo-child limit policy, including from
OL,9,Fwithin his own party, but he saw off
OL,10,Fhis first Commons rebellion on
OL,11,FTuesday, with the Government
OL,12,Fcomfortably defeating calls to scrap
OL,13,Fthe policy.
