OL,6,FOne of his MPs, Rosie Duffield,
OL,7,Fdescribed the limit as a "heinous
OL,8,Fpiece of legislation" and "a sinister
OL,9,Fand overtly sexist law" which drove
OL,10,Fher into politics, while John
OL,11,FMcDonnell called the policy an "attack
OL,12,Fon the poorest" and said his party
OL,13,Fshould plan to abolish it "within
OL,14,Fweeks".
OL,16,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,17,Fon Monday said it would be looked at
OL,18,F"as one of a number of ways" to lift
OL,19,Fchildren out of poverty, with Labour
OL,20,Fhaving set up a new taskforce to
OL,21,Ftackle child poverty.
