OL,6,FBut Sir Keir has said there is no
OL,7,F"silver bullet" and that there was a
OL,8,F"complicated set of factors" including
OL,9,Fpay, benefits, work, housing,
OL,10,Feducation and health at play.
OL,12,FIn their report, the charities said:
OL,13,F"Money and mental health are
OL,14,Finextricably linked; not having enough
OL,15,Fmoney leads to parental stress and
OL,16,Fguilt, which has a knock-on impact on
OL,17,Fchildren, both in the here and now and
OL,18,Fover the course of their lives."
