OL,6,FThe latest official UK figures,
OL,7,Fpublished earlier this year, showed an
OL,8,Festimated 4.33 million children in
OL,9,Fhouseholds in relative low income
OL,10,Fafter housing costs in the year to
OL,11,FMarch 2023 ` a record high.
OL,13,FThe charities said poverty is "a
OL,14,Fcritical risk factor" which has
OL,15,F"surged alongside this rise in mental
OL,16,Fill health" in recent years.
