OL,6,FTheir requests to Government include
OL,7,Frepeating a call for a so-called
OL,8,F"child lock" by double-locking
OL,9,Fchildren's social security
OL,10,Fentitlements to increase by earnings
OL,11,For inflation; scrapping the two-child
OL,12,Flimit and benefit cap; reforming
OL,13,Fconditionality within Universal Credit
OL,14,Fto ensure claimants with health
OL,15,Fconditions, single parents, and
OL,16,Fparents of young children are exempt
OL,17,Ffrom sanctions; and improving
OL,18,Femployment support for families
OL,19,Fthrough specialist work coaches for
OL,20,Fparents.
