OL,4,Cof poverty and mental health'
OL,6,FAndy Bell, chief executive at the
OL,7,FCentre for Mental Health, said:
OL,8,F"Poverty casts a shadow over a child's
OL,9,Fmental health, and it's a shadow that
OL,10,Fcan last a lifetime.
OL,12,F"Effective action from the Government
OL,13,Fcan start to turn this around."
OL,15,FPriya Edwards, policy and advocacy
OL,16,Fadviser at Save the Children UK, said:
OL,17,F"A childhood blighted by poverty and
OL,18,Fpoor mental health leads to dreadful
OL,19,Foutcomes for young people that sadly
OL,20,Fimpacts them for the rest of their
OL,21,Flife.
